                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Do you like primarily sci-fi or fantasy games?  With the Rhizom statement, I can tell you don't like both at the same time  <img src="images/smiles/icon_razz.gif" alt="icon_razz.gif" border="0" /> 
<br />

<br />
Anyway, if you like sci-fi, you could try out Matrix. I was in the beta a long time ago when the game was far more buggy, but they've come a long way and a few friends who play really enjoy it.  Other than that, I feel you pretty much captured the universe (other than Kingdom of Loathing, of course, but I doubt you meant _that_ kind of entertainment)</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><img src="http://www.therambler.net/images/sigs/devon2.jpg" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
